description:
Team Foundation Sidekicks is a suite of tools for Microsoft Team Foundation Server administrators and advanced users providing Graphic User Interface for administrative and advanced version control tasks in multi-user TFS environment.
Version 3.1 of Team Foundation Sidekicks is available for Visual Studio 2012 and TFS 2012.
| Please install with chocolatey (http://nuget.org/List/Packages/chocolatey).
